'''Ginger''' is the stripper Cooper hired for Sam who was treated by Pete for a rash.

==History==
Winging to get Sam back into the game, Cooper hired a stripper to come to his house and perform for him. Sam let Ginger in and she began to dance. However, while she was dancing, he noticed a rash on her right buttock. He sent her to Pete for treatment.

==Career==
Ginger is a entertainer. She can be hired to go to people's homes to dance for them.
